name: Shapes of a Heart Chakra
description: A collaboration between myself the artist Zack Prestage and model Okamii Daniels for the Shapes of the Divine project.   When you buy my NFTs  from this collection every  3-6 months I will be making a donation to the local battered women shelters of 10% of each sale   Shapes of the Divine, is a project about body positivity and empowerment of the humans regardless of what their pronouns are or who or what they identify as. It is all inclusive regardless of, size, weight, race or religion. being published as a coffee book of beautiful people
